-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SPad

A simple text-editor using Qt(v.4.7.4 ).
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

What's in the name?
Well SPad basically means SuperPad. It can also means ScratchPad or SillyPad.

Objective of this project:
To learn more about desktop and GUI development on my sparetime.

